WEBVTT

00:00.917 --> 00:02.377
Ah-hyuck!

00:02.460 --> 00:04.546
♪ H-h-h-hit it ♪

00:04.629 --> 00:06.381
♪ Like father, like son ♪

00:07.298 --> 00:08.591
♪ You're always number one ♪

00:08.675 --> 00:09.676
[both]
Yes!

00:09.759 --> 00:11.511
♪ There's buddies
There's pals ♪

00:11.594 --> 00:12.470
Yeah!

00:12.554 --> 00:14.848
♪ You always seem to work things out ♪

00:14.931 --> 00:16.641
♪ Can't you see you're two of a kind ♪

00:16.725 --> 00:18.727
♪ Lookin' for a real good time ♪

00:18.810 --> 00:19.644
Whoa!

00:20.311 --> 00:21.271
♪ A real good time ♪

00:21.354 --> 00:22.272
Aah!

00:22.689 --> 00:24.232
♪ Report to the Goof Troop ♪

00:24.315 --> 00:26.526
♪ And we'll always stick together ♪

00:26.609 --> 00:27.694
♪ Always stick together ♪

00:27.777 --> 00:29.362
♪ We're the Goof Troop ♪

00:29.446 --> 00:31.781
♪ The best of friends forever ♪

00:33.116 --> 00:35.493
♪ Side by side wherever we go ♪

00:35.577 --> 00:39.914
♪ We're always ready to roll ♪

00:39.998 --> 00:41.249
♪ Now gimme a beat ♪

00:41.332 --> 00:42.792
♪ We're the Goof Troop ♪

00:42.876 --> 00:45.462
♪ And we always stick together ♪

00:45.545 --> 00:46.379
Gawrsh!

00:46.463 --> 00:47.339
♪ We're the Goof Troop ♪

00:47.422 --> 00:50.550
♪ The best of friends forever ♪

00:51.468 --> 00:53.845
♪ Now we're calling everyone ♪

00:53.928 --> 00:55.889
♪ Come along and join the fun ♪

00:55.972 --> 00:56.973
♪ Report to the Goof Troop ♪

00:57.057 --> 00:58.850
♪ Baa ba doo da bop baa ba doo bop ♪

00:58.933 --> 00:59.809
Yeah!

01:05.523 --> 01:07.442
Max, I need your duffel bag.

01:07.525 --> 01:10.153
-Coming. Catch, P.J.
-What?

01:10.236 --> 01:14.366
Oh, but, Walnut Shell,
you're only going away for a weekend.

01:14.699 --> 01:16.034
Why do you need the dog?

01:16.117 --> 01:20.663
Goosebumps, what if we run into a herd
of marauding chipmunks?

01:20.747 --> 01:22.999
[growling]

01:23.083 --> 01:25.960
Rabies on your family tree.

01:26.044 --> 01:30.173
[both] One, two... three...

01:30.256 --> 01:31.758
I got it! I got it!

01:32.676 --> 01:35.011
Oops. Ah-hyuck!

01:36.262 --> 01:37.847
My van!

01:37.931 --> 01:40.141
No. My van.

01:40.225 --> 01:41.893
You can put a sunroof when we get back.

01:41.976 --> 01:43.645
Now, pick up the dog!

01:43.728 --> 01:45.855
Have you boys seen Pistol?

01:50.902 --> 01:53.154
Well, for goodness' sakes!

01:53.238 --> 01:54.989
How'd you get in there?

01:55.073 --> 01:56.700
An unidentified person

01:56.783 --> 02:00.662
whose initials are P.J.
kept shoving junk in the backseat.

02:00.745 --> 02:02.038
[whistling]

02:02.122 --> 02:04.290
Rather thoughtlessly, I might add.

02:04.374 --> 02:06.042
Just ask Waffles.

02:06.126 --> 02:07.168
[meows]

02:07.585 --> 02:10.171
OK. Everybody in.

02:10.255 --> 02:11.381
[P.J.] I got shotgun!

02:11.506 --> 02:12.632
[overlapping chatter]

02:17.137 --> 02:18.471
Quiet!

02:21.891 --> 02:26.312
Now, dimple knees, try and be friendly
with Goofy while we're gone... [chuckles]

02:26.396 --> 02:27.230
Or else!

02:27.313 --> 02:29.399
Uh... Yes, cookie tin.

02:29.482 --> 02:31.735
Drive safely, Snookums.

02:32.527 --> 02:34.029
-Miss you. Love you.
-Miss you.

02:34.112 --> 02:35.572
[Peg] Miss you. Love you.

02:35.655 --> 02:36.614
[kissing]

02:36.698 --> 02:39.617
-Be careful, son.
-So long, kids!

02:39.701 --> 02:41.369
-[Max] Bye, Dad!
-Bye, Dad!

02:42.620 --> 02:45.206
Bye. Bye-bye.

02:45.290 --> 02:46.499
Goodbye.

02:46.583 --> 02:48.501
Bye-bye.

02:48.585 --> 02:49.586
Gone!

02:49.669 --> 02:51.171
Ha ha ha!

02:54.591 --> 02:58.261
Ahhhh. Two days of peace and quiet.

03:00.722 --> 03:04.559
Well, neighbor, guess it's just
you and me now.

03:09.064 --> 03:10.482
Nothin' doin'.

03:10.565 --> 03:14.277
I'm spending my time alone... alone.

03:14.361 --> 03:16.780
But this is our big chance to get closer.

03:16.863 --> 03:17.864
Ah-hyuck!

03:17.947 --> 03:21.451
Like watch cartoons
and play Parcheesi till dawn.

03:21.534 --> 03:23.119
Scram.

03:27.791 --> 03:30.210
Waffles, better get down, girl.

03:30.293 --> 03:32.420
You know how Pete is about his boat.

03:32.587 --> 03:33.713
[meows]

03:42.222 --> 03:43.056
Uh-oh!

03:45.517 --> 03:46.518
Help!

03:46.601 --> 03:48.144
Pete! Save me!

03:48.770 --> 03:49.646
Ha ha ha!

03:49.729 --> 03:51.606
Screwball.

03:52.023 --> 03:53.191
My boat!

03:55.777 --> 03:56.778
-Ohhh!
-[cat meows]

03:59.864 --> 04:03.660
N-n-n-n-no!

04:03.743 --> 04:05.578
Whoa!

04:13.503 --> 04:18.425
Why... why, Pete! You saved my life.

04:18.508 --> 04:19.551
Thanks!

04:20.260 --> 04:23.555
Yeah, yeah. All right, fine.
Don't slobber on me. [murmurs]

04:29.144 --> 04:30.020
Oh, Pete?

04:30.103 --> 04:30.979
Ugh.

04:31.813 --> 04:33.356
How'd you get in here?

04:33.440 --> 04:36.818
Your attic window was open.
Here, I brought you a present.

04:36.901 --> 04:39.988
[chuckles] My very first model kit.

04:40.071 --> 04:43.742
Oh, I don't want these stupid things.

04:43.825 --> 04:45.952
My most prized possession, Pete.

04:46.036 --> 04:47.912
It's for saving my life.

04:47.996 --> 04:50.749
[grins] I was saving my boat.

04:50.832 --> 04:53.209
I owe you big, pal. Just name it.

04:54.419 --> 05:00.300
Well, OK. Go make me a sandwich,
then hit the bricks.

05:00.383 --> 05:01.968
Ah-hyuck! You got it.

05:02.802 --> 05:05.805
Hmm. Uhhh.

05:05.889 --> 05:07.182
-[shatters]
-Not bad.

05:07.265 --> 05:08.808
Ha ha ha!

05:15.065 --> 05:16.649
Bet he'd like some popcorn.

05:20.153 --> 05:22.864
Uh, don't forget the chips, Goofer.

05:22.947 --> 05:24.699
Okey-dokey.

05:25.241 --> 05:28.161
Oh. And a diet sody, too.

05:37.337 --> 05:39.089
[dings]

05:40.215 --> 05:41.216
[popping]

05:41.299 --> 05:44.886
Hmm. What's taking Einstein so long?

05:44.969 --> 05:47.764
[popping]

05:48.932 --> 05:51.059
Hey, what was tha--

05:51.142 --> 05:52.811
[dings]

06:02.737 --> 06:05.240
W-w-w-whoa ho!

06:05.323 --> 06:09.577
Gawrsh. What a mess.
Lemme clean it up for ya.

06:10.078 --> 06:15.291
No! Just go outside and-and
clean the rain gutters!

06:15.375 --> 06:17.293
No problem.

06:19.713 --> 06:23.883
Hmm. This is gonna take me till supper
to get rid of.

06:26.678 --> 06:30.807
[humming]

07:18.938 --> 07:19.856
Help!

07:19.939 --> 07:21.358
Help! [screams]

07:21.441 --> 07:23.026
Now what?

07:25.278 --> 07:26.446
Whoa!

07:31.534 --> 07:33.703
[groaning]

07:35.246 --> 07:38.583
Ahh. Safe at last.

07:38.667 --> 07:41.628
Pete! Look what I brought ya.

07:41.711 --> 07:43.380
Hey! I'm takin' a bath here!

07:43.463 --> 07:44.589
I know.

07:44.673 --> 07:46.508
That's why I brought Uncle Bubble.

07:46.591 --> 07:47.967
Industrial strength you know.

07:48.051 --> 07:49.844
Get outta here, dufus!

07:52.681 --> 07:53.973
[Goofy] Uh-oh.

07:54.057 --> 07:55.809
[Pete] You bubble head!

07:55.892 --> 07:57.060
[Goofy] Sorry.

07:58.728 --> 08:02.649
[snoring]

08:02.732 --> 08:04.943
-Ah-hyuck!
-[groaning]

08:05.026 --> 08:06.653
And this little piggy--

08:08.071 --> 08:09.739
What are you doin'?

08:09.989 --> 08:12.242
Trimmin' your toenails. Ah-hyuck!

08:12.325 --> 08:17.580
Why on earth would you be
trimmin' my toenails?

08:17.872 --> 08:19.457
'Cause I was done cuttin' your hair.

08:21.418 --> 08:23.211
Aah!

08:23.586 --> 08:24.421
Do you really like it?

08:24.504 --> 08:26.047
Be brutal.

08:26.131 --> 08:28.883
Whaa! Whoo whoo!

08:29.551 --> 08:31.553
He likes it. Ah-hyuck!

08:33.179 --> 08:34.180
[gibberish]

08:34.264 --> 08:35.223
Hello?

08:35.306 --> 08:37.600
Westwinds Travel Agency?

08:37.684 --> 08:39.185
Do you have deserted island trips?

08:40.395 --> 08:41.521
I'll take it!

08:42.605 --> 08:44.649
OK, I'll take this.

08:44.733 --> 08:47.777
Oh, yeah. [mumbling] A couple of those.

08:47.861 --> 08:50.488
[laughs] I'll make a clean getaway.

08:50.572 --> 08:52.282
[Goofy] Don't count on it, creep.

08:55.285 --> 08:58.955
Oh, gawrsh! I thought you was a burglar.

08:59.039 --> 09:00.123
Pete, say somethin'.

09:00.206 --> 09:04.836
Can we get the bunny
with the bent ear, Mama.

09:04.919 --> 09:07.589
Gee, Pete. What were you doin'
in the dark?

09:07.672 --> 09:13.345
I was plannin' a party. Yeah.
Party for you and me, buddy.

09:13.428 --> 09:16.556
Stay up all night and watch movies. 'Kay?

09:16.639 --> 09:17.474
Sounds great!

09:17.557 --> 09:19.726
Then you go make some popcorn.

09:19.809 --> 09:21.519
Lots and lots of popcorn.

09:21.603 --> 09:23.646
You're so good at that.

09:23.730 --> 09:27.233
I'm practically a pro. Ah-hyuck!

09:29.486 --> 09:32.280
[humming]

09:32.364 --> 09:34.949
Better clean this up first.

09:35.033 --> 09:40.038
By the time that corn-poppin' [mumbles]
moron gets back,

09:40.121 --> 09:41.915
I'll be snoozin' on the sand.

09:45.043 --> 09:47.003
Whoa!

09:47.087 --> 09:48.755
Whoooa! Look out!

09:51.091 --> 09:52.592
Goofy?

09:53.176 --> 09:54.761
Goofy?

09:55.595 --> 09:57.055
Yes!

10:00.725 --> 10:03.436
[engine starts]

10:05.271 --> 10:09.734
Freedom. [laughing]

10:12.320 --> 10:15.281
[Pete laughing]

10:17.200 --> 10:19.536
I'm alone. Yes! Except for you.

10:19.619 --> 10:22.122
But you're not Goofy. Ha ha ha.

10:22.205 --> 10:23.707
'Cause if you were, I'd throw you out
that little window.

10:23.790 --> 10:25.625
I'd stuff you up like this.
Woop, woop, woop. Ha!

10:25.709 --> 10:26.751
Throw you right out. But you're not.

10:26.835 --> 10:29.045
So I won't. Ha ha ha!

10:29.129 --> 10:30.422
Hey, these are good nuts.

10:31.756 --> 10:35.844
[scoffs] Hey. Where the heck am I?

10:37.137 --> 10:39.556
Pete's trunk. Hmm.

10:39.639 --> 10:41.391
Must be a door around here somewhere.

10:43.810 --> 10:44.644
Ow.

10:44.728 --> 10:48.398
Hey, Pete! Help! Get me outta here!

10:48.481 --> 10:51.317
Hey, open up! Help! Pete!

10:51.401 --> 10:52.652
It can't be.

10:52.736 --> 10:54.154
[Goofy] Save me, Pete!

10:55.238 --> 10:57.198
You stop that, you hear?

10:57.282 --> 10:58.616
Ooh, sorry.

10:58.700 --> 11:00.410
Must be turbulence.

11:04.205 --> 11:07.208
Whew! Gettin' kinda stuffy in here.

11:16.634 --> 11:18.053
Ohh! Dahh!

11:19.220 --> 11:21.222
Whaaaaaa!

11:21.890 --> 11:23.516
Leg cramps.

11:33.610 --> 11:36.321
You know why I like these?
'Cause they're not popcorn.

11:36.404 --> 11:37.530
Popcorn'll kill you.

11:37.614 --> 11:39.115
You're much safer with peanuts any day.

11:39.199 --> 11:40.617
[laughs]

11:41.368 --> 11:42.535
Fresh air.

11:46.539 --> 11:48.124
[crunch crunch]

11:48.208 --> 11:49.501
Peanuts?

11:53.421 --> 11:55.423
Hey, what gives?

11:58.927 --> 11:59.928
[belching]

12:00.011 --> 12:00.887
Oops.

12:01.054 --> 12:02.806
Ah-hyuck!

12:02.889 --> 12:04.140
Ah-hyuck?

12:04.224 --> 12:07.477
Aah! That laugh. Did you hear it?
Did you hear it? You heard it!

12:07.560 --> 12:09.145
What laugh? Ah-hyuck?

12:10.730 --> 12:12.649
Stewardess, I'm going nuts.

12:12.732 --> 12:14.275
What kinda nuts?

12:15.276 --> 12:16.736
Ah-hyuck! Ah-hyuck!

12:16.820 --> 12:18.613
Ah-hyuck! Ah-hyuck!

12:18.697 --> 12:20.031
Aah!

12:21.074 --> 12:24.744
Blb-blb-blb-blb-blb!

12:27.330 --> 12:29.290
[man] Are you all right?

12:29.374 --> 12:32.127
Be waking yourself up now.

12:32.210 --> 12:33.128
Huh.

12:33.837 --> 12:34.754
[grunts]

12:34.921 --> 12:36.423
I musta been dreamin'.

12:36.506 --> 12:38.383
Hey, mon.

12:38.466 --> 12:42.721
Relax... You're in da islands now.

12:42.804 --> 12:46.016
Yeah. You're right, buddy.

12:46.099 --> 12:49.019
Oh... Nothin' to bother me now.

12:49.602 --> 12:50.770
Yow!

12:53.815 --> 12:55.525
Duh, w-w-w...

12:55.608 --> 12:57.027
What was that?

12:57.944 --> 13:02.198
Da most fearsome shark
in these waters, yeah.

13:02.782 --> 13:08.288
Very bad fish, mon.
The locals call him jimbobbo royzara.

13:08.371 --> 13:12.667
And now he havin' a taste for you, mon.

13:12.751 --> 13:16.338
Eh...
But you on vacation now, don't ya know.

13:16.421 --> 13:19.799
So don't worry. Be happy, mon.

13:20.383 --> 13:22.177
There you go, mon.

13:22.260 --> 13:26.306
A hundred miles from no civilization.

13:26.765 --> 13:31.019
No one around, mon. No one around.

13:32.604 --> 13:35.940
Oh, at last. Away from everything...

13:36.024 --> 13:38.026
And everybody.

13:38.109 --> 13:40.653
Hey! Long time no see.

13:40.737 --> 13:41.780
Ah-hyuck!

13:41.863 --> 13:44.157
Aaah! I'm gonna pulverize ya!

13:44.824 --> 13:47.744
Want the last cookie? Ah-hyuck!

13:48.870 --> 13:52.832
-[Pete] My food!
-And it was delicious.

13:56.836 --> 13:59.506
-Yes, it's just the two of us, pal.
-Oh.

13:59.589 --> 14:01.966
[Goofy] Wait! Come back!

14:03.760 --> 14:06.179
Aaah!

14:08.765 --> 14:11.851
Whoa. Pretty mean goldfish.

14:11.935 --> 14:12.852
How can I get rid of you?

14:13.770 --> 14:15.730
You can't. You saved my life.

14:15.814 --> 14:17.482
So? We all make mistakes.

14:17.565 --> 14:19.192
Ancient folklore.

14:19.275 --> 14:21.444
I'm in your debt till I can pay you back.

14:21.528 --> 14:22.862
Now, let me get this straight.

14:23.279 --> 14:24.781
I saved your life...

14:24.864 --> 14:25.949
Uh-huh.

14:26.032 --> 14:29.285
...so you won't go away
till you can save mine?

14:29.369 --> 14:30.203
Bingo.

14:31.121 --> 14:32.038
Wait right here.

14:35.250 --> 14:37.002
Help. Goofy.

14:37.085 --> 14:38.545
Oh, save me.

14:38.628 --> 14:40.755
Help. Help. Oh, help.

14:40.839 --> 14:43.925
Where is that goof-off? Save me, Goofy!

14:44.009 --> 14:46.261
Hang on, Pete. I'm comin'!

14:47.012 --> 14:50.306
Ow! Ohh! The pain.

14:51.725 --> 14:53.435
Gawrsh, Pete, are you hurt?

14:54.185 --> 14:57.397
Aah. I fell, and I cannot get up.

14:57.480 --> 15:00.316
You'll have to save my life, pal.

15:04.487 --> 15:06.156
Tie this around ya.

15:08.992 --> 15:10.994
[strains] Uhh!

15:11.077 --> 15:11.953
Uhh!

15:17.083 --> 15:18.168
Ooph! Ow!

15:18.251 --> 15:19.210
Ohh!

15:22.797 --> 15:25.050
Mmm. Yum, yum, yum, yum.

15:25.133 --> 15:27.886
Him again? Faster, Goof. Faster!

15:27.969 --> 15:31.222
OK. Lemme get a better grip.

15:31.806 --> 15:34.267
Yeoooow!

15:34.351 --> 15:35.185
Oops.

15:35.268 --> 15:37.228
No! No! No! No! No!

15:42.734 --> 15:43.860
Hang on, Pete!

15:45.904 --> 15:47.030
Yeooow!

15:52.035 --> 15:52.994
Pete. Pete!

15:53.536 --> 15:54.996
You give my pal back!

15:55.413 --> 15:56.331
Help!

15:58.083 --> 15:59.042
Sorry.

16:00.335 --> 16:01.628
Aah!

16:01.711 --> 16:02.545
Ooph.

16:09.094 --> 16:11.638
Gawrsh. Sorry I couldn't save ya, Pete.

16:12.180 --> 16:13.431
Save me?

16:13.515 --> 16:16.059
You couldn't save table scraps for a dog!

16:17.352 --> 16:19.145
[chuckles] Oh, you don't mean that.

16:19.229 --> 16:20.939
Oh... But I do.

16:21.064 --> 16:24.150
I want you to leave me alone, understand?

16:24.234 --> 16:25.610
I'm sick of you savin' me.

16:25.735 --> 16:27.278
-Ow.
-And I'm sick of your

16:27.404 --> 16:28.738
"Uh-hyuck, Uh-hyuck!"

16:28.822 --> 16:31.366
Basically, I'm sick of you!

16:31.491 --> 16:32.742
But we're pals.

16:33.326 --> 16:34.244
Wrong!

16:34.327 --> 16:36.413
I want you as far away from me
as you can get.

16:36.496 --> 16:38.456
Now get off my island!

16:40.000 --> 16:41.668
But where will I live?

16:43.294 --> 16:44.587
Hmm.

16:44.671 --> 16:46.798
Ow! Ow!

16:46.881 --> 16:48.341
Oh, help, Goofy.

16:48.425 --> 16:50.218
I broke my foot.

16:51.219 --> 16:52.137
You OK?

16:52.721 --> 16:53.638
Ow.

16:53.722 --> 16:55.557
Boy, what a dipstick.

16:55.640 --> 16:58.101
Now, get! Go! Go for good!

17:25.795 --> 17:27.005
[sniffing]

17:27.130 --> 17:30.508
Ooh, yummy! [slurp]

17:30.592 --> 17:33.136
I thought I told you to beat it.

17:34.763 --> 17:35.638
Oops.

17:37.849 --> 17:39.601
Gaaah!

17:39.684 --> 17:42.729
Oh, nice fishy. Nice fin.

17:42.854 --> 17:44.647
How's the wife and kids?

17:44.773 --> 17:48.068
[blowing]

17:49.402 --> 17:51.529
[gasping]

17:53.656 --> 17:55.533
Yeow!

17:58.078 --> 17:59.788
[blowing]

18:14.552 --> 18:17.514
Uh, g-g-Goofy. A shark!

18:17.639 --> 18:19.015
Chop, chop. Frying pan!

18:19.140 --> 18:20.767
You gotta save me, pal.

18:21.393 --> 18:24.062
Uh-uh. I ain't fallin' for that again.

18:25.814 --> 18:27.273
Come back!

18:27.399 --> 18:28.733
Nothin' doin'.

18:28.817 --> 18:31.111
You can only fool me once or twice
or more.

18:34.823 --> 18:36.282
Aah!

18:51.297 --> 18:52.215
Uh-hyuck!

18:52.298 --> 18:54.050
What? Ow!

18:54.134 --> 18:56.344
Goofy, old pal, old buddy, old chum!

18:56.428 --> 18:58.888
No way. You're gonna hit me again.

18:59.014 --> 19:00.724
I won't hit ya. Promise.

19:00.807 --> 19:02.308
Look. I'll hit myself.

19:02.726 --> 19:03.727
See?

19:03.810 --> 19:04.728
Me, not you.

19:05.979 --> 19:08.023
Gawrsh. You really mean it.

19:08.148 --> 19:10.859
Yes. Now save me!

19:10.984 --> 19:11.901
Get in.

19:11.985 --> 19:12.944
Great.

19:13.737 --> 19:16.489
[whistling]

19:16.573 --> 19:18.450
Uh, ba bl-bl bl bl bl?

19:18.575 --> 19:20.368
What big fat guy?

19:20.493 --> 19:21.870
Bla bla dld blah.

19:21.995 --> 19:24.122
Nope. Haven't seen him. Try down river.

19:24.247 --> 19:25.123
Blo blay.

19:27.083 --> 19:28.293
He's gone.

19:28.418 --> 19:30.045
Great! Oh!

19:30.170 --> 19:31.713
Hey, it's locked.

19:31.838 --> 19:33.131
She's stuck, Pete.

19:33.214 --> 19:34.215
Hold on.

19:35.050 --> 19:36.509
Pry it open, dummy!

19:38.428 --> 19:39.429
Uhh!

19:39.512 --> 19:42.265
What the heck are you doin'?

19:43.975 --> 19:46.728
Oh. Don't move, Pete. I'll get ya.

19:46.853 --> 19:49.147
Float slowly. I'm comin'!

19:53.526 --> 19:56.071
[Pete] Hey, it's gettin' soggy in here!

19:56.154 --> 19:58.031
I want out! [sobs]

20:00.867 --> 20:03.078
I gotta do everything myself.

20:04.204 --> 20:05.538
Mama!

20:09.459 --> 20:10.585
Whew!

20:13.546 --> 20:14.506
[groans]

20:14.631 --> 20:17.342
Hang on, Petey boy! I'm comin'!

20:19.511 --> 20:21.304
Yum, yum, yum, yum!

20:23.306 --> 20:25.266
I made it!

20:25.558 --> 20:29.938
[both] W-w-w-whoa! W-w-w-whoa!

20:34.234 --> 20:35.068
Ptooey!

20:37.237 --> 20:38.905
[pants] Don't let him get me, Goof!

20:38.988 --> 20:40.407
Do somethin'.

20:40.490 --> 20:42.409
OK. Take off your shirt.

20:42.492 --> 20:43.868
Shirt. Right. Right.

20:47.622 --> 20:48.623
[belch]

20:51.584 --> 20:54.295
[pants] OK. Now the pants.

20:56.089 --> 20:57.215
You got it.

20:57.298 --> 20:59.217
I can't believe-- stupid.

21:04.889 --> 21:05.724
Now what?

21:05.807 --> 21:06.725
Jump in.

21:06.808 --> 21:07.851
OK.

21:08.143 --> 21:09.352
What?

21:09.477 --> 21:10.520
Sharks hate lava.

21:10.645 --> 21:12.605
I learned that in boy scouts.

21:12.731 --> 21:15.066
I'm not jumpin' into any volcano
and that's that.

21:15.150 --> 21:16.651
Uh-hyuck! I got it!

21:17.110 --> 21:18.528
Popcorn?

21:20.822 --> 21:22.032
No!

21:22.157 --> 21:24.534
[both] Yaah! Yaah!

21:26.494 --> 21:28.538
[Goofy] Uh-hyuck!

21:31.583 --> 21:34.085
Uh-hyuck! Well, guess we're even.

21:34.210 --> 21:37.797
[Pete] Even? Why, you...

21:39.215 --> 21:40.842
Aaaah!

21:40.967 --> 21:43.595
Hoo hoo!

21:51.686 --> 21:52.896
[Peg] Yoo-hoo!

21:53.021 --> 21:55.482
Pete, we're home.

21:56.691 --> 21:59.986
See, I knew you two could be pals.

22:00.070 --> 22:03.531
Next time I'll leave
you two here for a week.

22:05.909 --> 22:07.994
Oh, and look, kids.

22:08.119 --> 22:09.704
Daddy made dinner.

22:11.748 --> 22:13.249
♪ Gimme a beat ♪

22:13.333 --> 22:14.209
[theme music playing]

22:40.068 --> 22:40.902
Yeah!
